        <li>
          The project listed on RERA was only for one small block, not the
          entire township.
        </li>
        <li>
          The land for the remaining phases was still under acquisition and
          had pending approvals.
        </li>
        <li>
          The builder had been fined earlier for delayed projects.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        They stepped back from the booking, disappointed but safe. Sixteen
        months later, that project is stuck in limbo. Those 20 minutes probably
        saved them <strong>₹48 lakhs+</strong> and years of stress.
      </p>

